text:
The outfit this time,
isn't it a little unexpected?

... like the way the colors are used, or the overall feel...
all of those sorts of things.

It seems sort of different from the usual image
of 283Pro up until now.
I was thinking "We'll have outfits like this too, huh."

But I think something like this is totally fine.
Like we're moving in a new direction or something.
─ Like this is a new color for 283Pro?
To put it into words, yeah something like that.
